data.text:
2024-2025 Season: Save the Dates!

Our director Will Hillegeist is hard at work assembling a magnificent program for the 2024-2025 Season! For now, get out your calendar and block off these dates so you don’t miss our next three concerts: November 10, 2024, March 9, 2025 and May 18, 2025. Check back soon for all the details!

Subscribe to Our YouTube Channel!

Don’t miss the new release of one of our performance videos! Click here to jump to our YouTube channel then click “Subscribe.” You’ll be notified as soon as we put something up!

Follow PSW!

Are you interested in being a PSW Insider? You have options! And who doesn’t like options? Click “Contact Us” above to join our email list. We won’t spam you! Just one or two emails per concert cycle to let you know important dates, times and locations.

You can also follow our socials. Click the appropriate icon to go directly to our pages on YouTube, Facebook and Instagram:

2nd Annual PSW Composition Contest Coming Soon!

Our first Composition Contest was such a success, we thought an encore was in order! Check back this summer for application information!

Players Needed!

The Pennsylvania Symphonic Winds is in need of additional players! If you are a professional or dedicated amateur musician interested in sharing your passion to create exceptional musical performances, please contact our Personnel Manager at the email below for audition information. Rehearsals for our next performance will begin soon!

Email: psw.personnel.manager@gmail.com

Our Performances:

The Pennsylvania Symphonic Winds is a premier wind ensemble comprised of local musicians in the Philadelphia area. The membership of the PSW includes both professional and dedicated amateur musicians who share a passion to create exceptional musical performances.

The PSW plays a diverse repertoire of music, covering a wide range of styles. The PSW prides itself in possessing the advanced levels of musicality and technical proficiency most often found in professional ensembles.
